summary: I am a grant and knowledge manager working in the field of nature conservation and development,  with 5 years experience working for international NGOs, foundations, and research institutes the field of inclusive community-led conservation. I am also passionate about nature conservation and raising awareness on fragile ecosystems, endangered species and local conservation champions through visual storytelling and podcasting.
